These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, indonesian, french, british
1. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
2. the british is between the american and the indonesian##2
3. the british is on the right of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | american | british | indonesian | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, peas, blueberry, asparagus
1. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating peas is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | peas | apricot | asparagus | blueberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, superhero, comedy, action
1. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
2. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching action movies and the person watching superhero movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | action | comedy | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, volleyball, lacrosse, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | volleyball | cricket | skateboarding | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, climbing, skiing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | tennis | snowboarding | skiing | climbing |

