.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, italian, egyptian, malaysian
1. the italian is on the far right##1
2. the italian is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the egyptian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | australian | malaysian | italian |

