.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, helicopter, trike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | trike | helicopter | snowmobile | train |

