2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
4. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | cycling | tennis | lacrosse | surfing |

