.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, papaya, grapefruit, pepper
1. the person eating papaya is the person eating papaya##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | grapefruit | pepper | papaya | carrot |

